---
source: crates/runtime/tests/cluster/simple.rs
expression: "pretty.replace(tempdir.path().to_string_lossy().split_once('/').expect(\"should have leading /\").1,\n\"<TEMP_PATH>\")"
---
+------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type        | plan                                                                                                                                                                |
+------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan     | Sort: names.id ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                       |
|                  |   TableScan: names projection=[id, name, age, city, score]                                                                                                          |
| physical_plan    | SortExec: expr=[id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                                                 |
|                  |   DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[<TEMP_PATH>/test_simple_cluster_mode.csv]]}, projection=[id, name, age, city, score], file_type=csv, has_header=true   |
|                  |                                                                                                                                                                     |
| distributed_plan | =========ResolvedStage[stage_id=1.0, partitions=1]=========                                                                                                         |
|                  | ShuffleWriterExec: partitioning: None                                                                                                                               |
|                  |   SortExec: expr=[id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                                               |
|                  |     DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[<TEMP_PATH>/test_simple_cluster_mode.csv]]}, projection=[id, name, age, city, score], file_type=csv, has_header=true |
|                  |                                                                                                                                                                     |
|                  |                                                                                                                                                                     |
+------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
